data.description: This 1,293 sf home is located in the North Double Diamond Subdivision, 8 miles south of Alpine on Hwy 118.  Updated and features a split floorplan with 2 bedrooms and 2 large bathrooms, an open kitchen/dining/living area with a wood burning stove, 2 mini splits and a large 672 sf 2 Car Garage.  It sits on 6.76 acres of rolling hills with cedar and oaks and short grass high desert landscape with beautiful mountain views.
